{"block1":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You need some good information before you try to slow or <a href=\"http:\/\/hairgrowths.org\/hair-growth-information\/diet-hair-growth\/\"  >stop hair loss<\/a>. Read these tips for some great advice.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Massage the&nbsp;roots of&nbsp;your hair for a minimum of two minutes each day, to improve blood flow to the area. Doing so allows hair follicles to receive greater blood flow, minimizing your chances of losing hair. Do this massage at a time that is convenient for you, whether first thing in the morning, at bedtime, or in the shower under warm water.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aggressive styling and drying of wet hair is a bad idea. When hair is wet, it&#39;s more likely to suffer damage and break. If you want to keep the hair you still have, pat it gently dry with a soft towel and let air drying take care of the rest. Only style and comb your hair after it has completely dried.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"\/images\/portrait-of-a-male-mannequin-with-wig.jpg\" class=\" \" alt=\"portrait of a male mannequin with wig\"  \/>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">For men suffering from hair loss, consider using liquid <a href=\"http:\/\/www.webmd.com\/vitamins-supplements\/ingredientmono-971-saw%20palmetto.aspx?activeingredientid=971&activeingredientname=saw%20palmetto\"  >saw palmetto<\/a>. The natural extracts will work to stop DHT from growing, the male hormone that many believe to be the cause for hair loss. To do this,&nbsp;take the juice from the fruit and rub it&nbsp;on your head.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If your hair is gone, consider a wig. This is a wonderful way to deal with the loss of hair for both sexes. You can begin to lose your hair at any point in life, so young men should not feel ashamed if their hair begins to thin early. It has been known to strike even teenagers. As it becomes noticeable, a shorter cut may be more flattering. Short styles and shaved looks are considered attractive by many.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Use the above&nbsp;information on hair loss to help you regain a full head of hair. It may not&nbsp;happen right away, but with a little&nbsp;knowledge and understanding,&nbsp;your chances of seeing a nice thick head of hair are much greater.&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n"}